make C++ VBGMM that fit HLS.

## How to use
1. set parameter in setting.h

| parameter | role |
| --- | --- |
| N | data size |
| D | dimentionaly |
| K | init cluster number (not final cluster) |
| MAX\_ITER | upper bound of iteration of Variational EM |
| TOL | threshold of converge |
| REG\_COVOR | value for avoid Sk < 0 |
| RANDOM\_INIT | if 1 then its means will be initialized by random value |
| RANDOM\_SEED | seed of srand |
| DEBUG\_PRINT | if 1 then it output values for debuging |
| RESURT\_PRINT | if 1 then it output final values |
| ON\_CPU | if not 1 then it make ineffective any output |

$ /vbgmm [input_file_path]
